name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: mapreduce.jobhistory.joblist.cache.size
description: Size of the job list cache

name: hadoop.registry.zk.retry.times
description: Zookeeper connection retry count before failing

name: dfs.datanode.peer.metrics.min.outlier.detection.samples
description:
Minimum number of packet send samples which are required to qualify for outlier detection.
      If the number of samples is below this then outlier detection is skipped.

name: mapreduce.job.cache.limit.max-resources-mb
description:
The maximum size (in MB) a map reduce job is allowed to submit
    for localization via files, libjars, archives, and jobjar command line
    arguments and through the distributed cache. If set to 0 the limit is
    ignored.

name: mapreduce.map.cpu.vcores
description:
The number of virtual cores to request from the scheduler for
  each map task.

name: dfs.namenode.retrycache.expirytime.millis
description: The time for which retry cache entries are retained.
